channel.title: Making a Server
channel.description: Hello, i need help, i've tried to make a pserver literally over 20 times, i've failed each and everyone.... it's very upsetting. I want to make one more then anything, please can somebody help me make one, people say it's so quick to make all i need help with is getting a working source and file and getting it online, no coding, please if anyone has like 10 minutes free time please let me know it would be so much appreciated

item.title: Making a Server
item.dc:creator: @Tree Tree
item.description:
@Tree wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:2, topic:554756”]You realize that RSPS is entirely made up of Java (And some scripts), right? You’re going to have to learn to write it if you ever want to modify your server.

Other than that, be specific what you’re stuck on.[/quote]

He is throwing his hands up and asking us to do everything for him. That’s what’s happening, make no mistake.
